text: NYC #Democrats have released their numbers on #COVID19 epidemic there & the numbers are very reassuring. 192 deaths out of 15,592 cases for a case-fatality rate of just 1.23% - as I have long said, COVID-19 is just a really nasty flu; there's NO JUSTIFICATION for global shutdown. https://t.co/ebsJCyJIMh
